OL,3,CMan given three-year football banning
OL,4,Corder following incident ahead of match
OL,6,FA man has been given a three-year
OL,7,FFootball Banning Order following
OL,8,Fdisorder between supporters before a
OL,9,Fmatch in Reading.
OL,11,FGareth Whitehouse, 41, of Lee,
OL,12,FCardiff, appeared at Slough
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court on Tuesday 16 June,
OL,14,Fwhere he pleaded guilty to using
OL,15,Fthreatening or abusive words or
OL,16,Fbehaviour likely to cause harassment,
OL,17,Falarm or distress.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
