CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782213505
OL,3,CMan given three-year football banning
OL,4,Corder following incident ahead of match
OL,6,FAt around 1.45pm on 18 April 2026,
OL,7,FWhitehouse was involved in disorder
OL,8,Fbetween Reading FC and Cardiff City
OL,9,Fsupporters in Greyfriars Street,
OL,10,FReading, before the two sides played
OL,11,Feach other in League One.
OL,13,FHe was arrested and charged on the
OL,14,Fsame day.
OL,16,FIn addition to the Football Banning
OL,17,FOrder, Whitehouse was ordered to pay
OL,18,F#253 in fines and costs.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
