PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782213505
OL,3,CMan given three-year football banning
OL,4,Corder following incident ahead of match
OL,6,FFootball banning orders are designed
OL,7,Fto prevent further disorder and can
OL,8,Fplace strict conditions on
OL,9,Findividuals, including preventing them
OL,10,Ffrom attending matches and requiring
OL,11,Fthem to surrender passports during
OL,12,Fmajor international tournaments, such
OL,13,Fas the FIFA World Cup, to prevent
OL,14,Fthose with a history of disorder from
OL,15,Ftravelling abroad.
OL,17,FDedicated football officer for Reading
OL,18,FFC, PC Steve Mountain, said: "Disorder
OL,19,Fsuch as this has no place in football
OL,20,For in our communities.
OL,26,@zD@^OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
