OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782213505
OL,3,CMan given three-year football banning
OL,4,Corder following incident ahead of match
OL,6,F"The vast majority of supporters
OL,7,Fattend matches to enjoy the game
OL,8,Fsafely, and it is the actions of a
OL,9,Fsmall minority that risk spoiling that
OL,10,Fexperience for others.
OL,12,F"With major international tournaments
OL,13,Fsuch as the World Cup attracting
OL,14,Fglobal attention, Football Banning
OL,15,FOrders play a crucial role in
OL,16,Fpreventing known offenders from
OL,17,Ftravelling overseas and becoming
OL,18,Finvolved in disorder.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
