OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1782213505
OL,3,CMan given three-year football banning
OL,4,Corder following incident ahead of match
OL,6,F"This result demonstrates our
OL,7,Fcommitment to working with clubs and
OL,8,Fpartners to identify those involved in
OL,9,Fanti-social and criminal behaviour and
OL,10,Fensure they are held accountable."
